Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:33.00,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便可以拭去你的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:39.06,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而讓你流淚的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:45.91,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻一定無法僅用這雙手來承受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:51.07,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不見的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:56.22,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們緊緊聯系在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:59.40,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用心去感受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.51,0:22:03.31,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力深呼吸（深呼吸）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:09.10,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試著去深呼吸的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:13.05,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是獨自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.36,0:22:16.05,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對無法跨越的屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:21.06,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 只要和你一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:26.93,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼困難都能跨越
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:32.94,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能繼續努力下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.61,0:00:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西區的「狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.91,0:00:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其稱號的情報基本已經收集完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還有一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「湖之麗人」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著莪菖蒲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止似乎還沒有泄露我們的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在監視區域之外傳播的可能性呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女她們在活動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泄露了的話應該會有所動作才對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 我直接去一趟會更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會造成全面抗爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們恐怕也會承受重大損失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死多少匹「狼」對我來說一點都不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就乖乖給我繼續監視麗人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一場鬧劇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我們是為了什麼才甘愿淪為「狗」的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.33,0:00:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.31,0:00:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「加百列的棘齒」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.31,0:00:57.45,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}加百列：圣經中負責向神傳達信息的大天使，被稱為“上帝的左手”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自行限制生存方式的落魄的「狗」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是現在的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.54,0:01:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#05北海道鮭魚魚骨味增湯 326kcal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤那家伙 真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 所以說...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和這裡的學生著莪菖蒲一起的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平易近人 對像我這樣的大叔都會每天早上打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 總有一天會有些自作多情的笨蛋跑出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 所以說我說了好多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰說什麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲醬就由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來教教你們接近她會有多危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是塞進裏面去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞進去！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗人正企圖與堂弟佐藤洋接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 估計兩人是打算一起去狩獵便當
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 狩獵場還沒弄清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？佐藤嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙大概1個多小時以前在校門前面被警衛帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:03:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑 我來塞進去！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 發生什麼事了 二階堂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來麗人和佐藤打算去拉爾夫便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤帶著傳單
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你先過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下 我們的計劃的最終目的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消滅佐藤是計劃的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 佐藤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來 你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是搞什麼 是快被搞定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上手機跑已經是用盡全力的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 拜託給我弄套衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急情況 哇~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們追過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你現在在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥你們要追著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:04:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:05:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑啊 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 衣服什麼的一件也沒...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小鬼跑哪裡去了 我來塞進去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著莪 慢死了 快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變態 好變態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屈辱啊 為什麼我要...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借你個好東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下啦 坐下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個就能蓋住頭發 沒問題的 能行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...這是怎麼個能行...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一樣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 花紋是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:05:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是井上馬醉木 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬醉木
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去自動販賣機買咖啡回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 我請你喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 突然間就...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 吃醋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 我可是救了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 和馬醉木扯上關系你就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的不幸會降臨到你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？不幸？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是超自然現象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說你不也碰到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護身符？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:07:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬醉木身上纏著一股神佛都唯恐避之不及的不幸氣場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為啥突然間桌腳斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥這種地方會有圖釘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 剛才給你戴上帽子的時候碰到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之早點遠離這裡比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也快到貼半價貼紙的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 鞋的話隨便到鞋柜拿雙涼鞋...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...不如去第二家超市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來前天有說過吧 拉爾夫便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得從學姐手上拿到傳單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？學姐給的傳單去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 難得從學姐手上拿到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來吧 學姐的傳單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 馬醉木她呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 她的話一定不會回來的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停不下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還不是咖啡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是可樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以隨便喝耶 好涼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子一直在感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你發現了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 所以才圍著圍巾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人沒有覺得不幸也算是唯一的救贖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還和我的菖蒲醬親密地走在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有種啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑起來 佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來拖住大叔 你趕快去拉爾夫便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹輪我拿走了 還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收您10000零30日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不不不 這個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不知道啦 現在男生也會穿成這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說學姐你為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才是齋藤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想承認是我對手的男人竟然會是這等變態
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是不打算對別人的興趣多管閑事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 學姐你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變態 變態 變態...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候說可愛的話算是贊美吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說這是著莪那家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別慌慌張張的 真不像樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 不管怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOOD JOB
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...這當中有著復雜的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有要跟你這種人說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼一瞬間肯定了你的我真是蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 那個...也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這種人就等著被「帝王」打垮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...為啥那個人會...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 「帝王」是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「帝王」是指以這家店為地盤的「狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為求勝利不惜用盡卑鄙手段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的「狼」也認定他很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的「狼」在...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是「帝王」的地盤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以稱為西區「狼」的代表的你都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和「帝王」之間形成抗爭的話要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無意引起和那家伙的爭端
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大北海道展覽會？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 今天早上拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量使用北海道食材的珍稀便當嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這周周五起3天的限定期間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 像這樣的便當在變成半價以前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能剩下來都是個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 著莪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？白粉的校服？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我過去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 說起來...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 這個可以說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 讓她也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你知道東區的拉爾夫便利店嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啦 肯定知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還校服之余順便...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了確保什麼都不知道的佐藤不會向「帝王」出手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過來看看情況而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 專門為了我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 難道說對我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 那個...怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對這種事也不怎麼在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的生活方式嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說那個...不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤同學 拿出自信來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什麼都不明白...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？你說什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個 這家店的半價神來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人？而且還很年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松葉菊 人稱小松
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年以前還是相當有名的「狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後現在成了半價神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如學姐所說 北海道展覽會剩下的就只有那些嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說也有幾個普通的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的目標果然還是石狩鮭魚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要鰻魚魚子便當
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著莪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是魔女的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 你也是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊 麗人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 勝負已分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人？呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 變態
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能讓你拿到便當
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是「加百列的棘齒」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「帝王」忠實的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「加百列的棘齒」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 那群人的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來就像是只為了攔住佐藤一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女養的「狗」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜你將會在歷史留名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到光榮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「帝王」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 已經分出勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把這男人當作東區和西區全面抗爭的祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「帝王」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 「湖之麗人」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這只沒用的雜種狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜種狗只要乖乖地被我玩弄於股掌之上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決出最強之名的戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的血化為開戰的狼煙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒過來後發現 我和不認識的女性在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:15:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說我在不知不覺間登上了大人的階梯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 安定下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我預想的要快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 很快嗎我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不 不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...雖然我記不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我果然是打了一仗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果雖然很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以有下次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨我記不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨自己的經驗不足到讓對方說結果很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來對方是人妻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果丈夫在這時候出現的話就成修羅場了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我就這樣退縮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不管是快還是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用次數來彌補的話就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:17:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 還是年輕氣盛的我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 起來吧 我的小弟弟...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤 起來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是一直不醒的話 就只能背著你回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？臉色很差哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因為「帝王」的攻擊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「帝王」？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你記憶有點混亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是拉爾夫便利店的休息室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應半價神的好意 讓被「帝王」打倒的你在這裡休息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這麼說起來...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我把衣服帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快換上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個...我有點難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能的話請你們兩位...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒什麼比你這幅樣子要更讓人難為情的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快換上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個...不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說我現在起不來...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 腳受傷了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 學姐 那裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？難道說...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:17:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 發生什麼事了？發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 只有我被排斥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就能起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從某種意義上來說已經起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 雖說買是買了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過咖啡過濾器有好幾種
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一 我買了3種...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 一共多少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把全部人變成男人的話能用得上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只剩下這個了 不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 能請我吃東西已經很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃晚餐之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗人 我有事情想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和「帝王」是有什麼關系的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也說不上什麼關系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:18:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 就告訴你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「帝王」打算把這條街的所有超市納入支配范圍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎麼一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西區占領作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天算起 3天後的北海道展覽會最後一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以「加百列的棘齒」為中心的西區的「狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會襲擊西區的所有超市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 「帝王」打算一次過算清以前的舊賬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的舊賬？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說被稱為東區最強的「狼」以前敗給了西區的「狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「帝王」對此事依然懷恨在心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來我是打算一跟佐藤重逢就馬上說出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我又想 不如就先不說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也參與了那個計劃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明知「帝王」埋伏在這裡 還是把佐藤帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 那真的只是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼不早點說出計劃的事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為佐藤他...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤他...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？我做什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手放在胸前好好想想 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們也得想個對策
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊在3天後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤 白粉 我需要你們的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是東區的「狼」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡的話事情也不好說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你還在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有可能被盯上了 應該避免單獨行動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦 看來對他們而言我就是只個棄子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著莪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那家伙罵我說雜種狗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個我不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因為我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「寒冰魔女」開始聯系西區的「狼」了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:22:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來麗人總算把我們的情報散布出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.37,0:22:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 從現在到作戰開始為止的3天之內
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓任何人靠近這個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:22:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了在外面上鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種空腹感在3天後就會成為最強的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.42,0:23:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要奪回最強之名
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.25,0:23:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.04,0:23:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集的肌肉刑警是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.08,0:23:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集齋藤也會被狂上...
